---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="5-Minute Wins">
  <article>
    <h1>5-Minute Wins</h1>
    <p class="subtitle" style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-style: italic; color: var(--color-text-muted);">
      The smallest action that moves the needle. Every morning, guaranteed.
    </p>

    <h2>Visibility — 1 to 3 minutes each</h2>
    <ul style="width: var(--content-width); padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <li>Comment on 1 relevant LinkedIn post with insight</li>
      <li>Share a skill demo screenshot with one-line caption</li>
      <li>Reply to a DM with a helpful link</li>
      <li>Repost someone's content with a short take</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Engagement — 2 to 5 minutes each</h2>
    <ul style="width: var(--content-width); padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <li>Send a follow-up to a warm lead</li>
      <li>Thank someone who shared your content</li>
      <li>Introduce two people who should know each other</li>
      <li>Ask a genuine question in a relevant community</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Content — 5 to 10 minutes each</h2>
    <ul style="width: var(--content-width); padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <li>Record a 2-minute Loom of one skill in action</li>
      <li>Write 3 LinkedIn post drafts (headlines only)</li>
      <li>Turn an agent research output into a quick post</li>
      <li>Screenshot a cool result and add context</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Sales — 3 to 5 minutes each</h2>
    <ul style="width: var(--content-width); padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <li>Review one agent-researched lead profile</li>
      <li>Send one "saw this, thought of you" message</li>
      <li>Update one case study with recent data</li>
      <li>Draft one sentence of a testimonial request</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Rules</h2>
    <ol style="width: var(--content-width); padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <li>Dashboard always has at least one 5-min item</li>
      <li>Do the 5-min item BEFORE opening Telegram</li>
      <li>After completing, mark done — streak visible</li>
      <li>If you do only the 5-min item today, that's enough</li>
    </ol>
  </article>
</Base>
